profile:
Concrete Fusion provides professional polished concrete and epoxy flooring services for residential, commercial and industrial needs for any specific flooring requirement. To deliver high quality and lasting results, we work with some well-proven polished concrete and epoxy coating products, and utilize state of the art equipment. We offer complete support to our customers with material selection, specification, installation and post-installation follow-up.

Concrete Fusion is the leading service provider for any Polished Concrete, Epoxy Flooring & Concrete Repair Services across Ottawa & Eastern Ontario.

To assist your various needs, our company is happy to offer a full range of services including: Polished Concrete, Epoxy Coatings- Seamless Flooring, Decorative Concrete Flooring, Moisture Vapour Control Flooring, Concrete Repair, Surface Preparation, New Concrete Installation, and Self Leveling Concrete.
